
0-installation-script

Step 1: Install Node.js v20.16 as follows
curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

Step 2: Exit the terminal using the exit command then reopen it.

Step 3: Verify Node.js installation with node -v.

Step 4: Install SASS version 3.7.4 using npm install sass -v 3.7.4

Step 5: Verify Sass installation with npm sass --version
